{
  "stem": "2004.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But in the ghetto, as we were selecting these things-- now subsequently, on a later date, I one more time was able to find another gold coin.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And again, we went through the same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we got some more food, which lasted us for-- for a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Now, I was-- now we are-- and that was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I wasn't always working at the same detail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was working in other details, as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I was now working-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] actually, I think that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] coming to the early fall of 1943-- by early fall, I mean probably around September-- they needed-- the Jewish committee decided-- they did not decide, but they got an order from the Germans that they have to send a group of people to a labor camp, which was, I would say, about an hour away from Jesow.",
      "word_count": 73
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The name of that labor camp was Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Pustkow was a small concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Basically, really, up to this day, I don't know the difference between a labor camp and a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I presume a labor camp was a camp which did not have a crematoria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Concentration camps-- the large ones-- always had a crematoria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But this one was-- and we'll call it-- I will call it a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Basically, the treatment and everything else was identical with a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "By the way, that labor camp in Pustkow was rather feared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because it was notorious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was very, very, a very bad camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There were certain camps which are known, at the time, as good camps-- so-called good camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And there were some which were called very bad camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Now, Pustkow had the reputation of being a bad camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
